    "Figure 5.5• Explainable AI (XAI): After individuals provide their predictions, they receive AI recommendations (along with feature contributionbased explanations) and then make their final judgments (see Figure10in Appendix).",
    "Figure 5:5Figure 5: The interface of Deliberative AI."
